Description:
This is my first attempt of creating a beautiful female character for Skyrim. This one is a blonde Imperial. I have used a few beautification mods to get this look. Below are the mods. It\'s about a minute into the game, just outside the Helgren cave entrance at the first sign post you come across.

Mods Used:
Better Females by Bella by BellaGail (Makeup v2)
No More Blocky Faces by Xenius
